title: Maryam Nawaz wins PP-159 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Maryam Nawaz of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-159 Lahore-XV by securing 23,598 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, her runner-up was independent candidate Mehar Sharafat Ali, who bagged 21,491 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn-out remained 36.55 %.
